summary:
Tony: Nat, in your opinion, how would I die?
Natasha, completely deadpan: Murder. Someone got real pissed at you. Full on...
body:
Tony: Nat, in your opinion, how would I die?
Natasha, completely deadpan: Murder. Someone got real pissed at you. Full on beheading. The police only find your body. No head.
Tony: Huh.
Clint, from the other side of the room: *silently raises his hand in question*
Natasha, without looking up: You trip down the stairs.
Clint, quietly: Dammit.

summary: Ametrine Gem!AU Tony is finally finished to my satisfaction :D (Though I did have trouble deciding between the two versions - on...
caption:
Ametrine Gem!AU Tony is finally finished to my satisfaction :D

(Though I did have trouble deciding between the two versions - on the left his armor is more pink, and on the right, more purple - so i decided to post both ^^)

I really, really love how this turned out *heart eyes* like, the lines are smooth, the colors are bright and soft, the design is really cute and everything turned out really clean and soft :3  …and this all started with a doodle i did at 2 am that i was deeply unhappy with originally! :L
